{"article_id":"Binz4Cz39IZIO9qV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"TEL AVIV , Israel -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Initial vote counting shows no clear winner in Israel 's historic election just yet .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Israel 's Kan public broadcaster reports","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu 's Likud party and Benny Gantz 's rival Blue and White party are neck-and-neck .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Three surveys also show","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that Netanyahu did not earn enough seats in the Knesset","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to form a right-wing majority government coalition","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"without Blue and White or Avigdor Liberman 's Yisrael Beytenu party .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"An exit poll on Channel 12 says","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Likud and the Blue and White party are tied with 32 seats each .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Official results are not expected to be announced until Wednesday afternoon local time .","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"\" We ' re still waiting for the results .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"But one thing is clear ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"the State of Israel is at a historic turning point .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"We are facing immense opportunities and immense challenges...","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"including the existential threat from Iran , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Netanyahu told supporters early Wednesday morning at the Likud election headquarters in Tel Aviv .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Netanyahu also said","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Israel will never have a government ``","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that leans on Arab , anti-Zionist parties . '' `` We were busy with the campaign for too long .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"And with your permission , we will be waiting for another day or two","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and we wish the people of Israel a good and desirable unity government , ''","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Gantz said .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Tuesday ' s election is said to be a referendum on Netanyahu ,","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"who has served as Israel ' s longest-running prime minister .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"This is an unprecedented election","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"because it is the first time","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Israel has held elections twice in the same year .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Netanyahu 's Likud party won the election in April","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"but the prime minister ' s inability","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to form a government coalition weeks after the election","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"sent millions of Israelis back to the polls on Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"After casting his ballot in Jerusalem ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Netanyahu said","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"the vote would be `` very close . ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"`` It 's not in the bag .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"if you go","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"( vote ) ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"we will win , ''","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Netanyahu told Israelis in Jerusalem .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Gantz voted in his hometown of Rosh Haayin","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and asked fellow Israelis to end Netanyahu ' s long reign as prime minister .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"`` We will bring hope ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"we will bring change ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"without corruption , without extremism , ''","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"There was plenty of drama","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"as Israelis made their ways to the polls .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Police say","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"they made at least 29 arrests","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and 69 investigations were launched against individuals","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"suspected of voting fraud and other violations .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Police reported","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that voting slips were vandalized ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"several people illegally filmed inside the voting booths ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"and one man cut the power at a polling site","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"and stole several voting slips .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"One suspect even threw a firework outside a polling station outside Jerusalem .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Israeli media also reported","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that the Blue and White website was shut down due to a cyberattack","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"hours before polls closed .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"The party said","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"the \" significant cyberattack \" was carried out in a wide-scale operation .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"\" Over 500 attempted breaches were detected from various servers abroad , \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"the party said .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Despite the drama ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"both Likud and Blue and White are cautious not to celebrate any perceived victory too early .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Party leaders are waiting for the final vote to be counted .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Official results will only come out in the next week","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and forming a government can take another month or more after that .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"If no government is formed","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Israelis will go to a third round of elections .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"For now , Israelis are waiting to see","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"if a government is formed","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and what it will look like .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":97,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":85,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":84,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nucle